# I rules with correctons

0BEGIN.0 I is|be|are::word=I am::pivots=\1,am

# You rules with corrections

We|They|You is|am::word=\0 are::pivots=\1,are
We|They|You was::word=\0 were::pivots=\1,were
0BEGIN.0 I has::word=\0 have::pivots=\1,have
We|They|You has::word=\0 have::pivots=\1,have

# He/She rules with corrections

0BEGIN.0 I were::word=\0 was::pivots=\1,was
He|She were::word=\0 was::pivots=\1,was
He|She have::word=\0 has::pivots=\1,has
He|She be|am|are::word=\0 is::pivots=\1,is

